{"author":"Joe Oakhart","author_email":"joeoakhart+bot@navapbc.com","author_id":"594c-9dcf-5ad6-4e6d","data":{"fields":{"description":"## Why\n\nEnforcement is the goal of the epic, landing **only after** every writer signs (local,\nGitHub Actions, Gerrit stories) and grandfathering is proven (grandfathering story). Flipping\nearly turns every push red by construction (bug 27ae). This is the final, atomic switch — and\nthe **only** change that writes both the flag and `enforce_since`.\n\n## What\n\n- In `rebar.toml`, in **one** change, set `[identity] require_authenticated = true` **and**\n  `enforce_since = <the anchor SHA documented by the grandfathering story>`.\n- Demonstrate enforcement is real, and that each writer surface still passes **under**\n  enforcement.\n- Provide a documented fast-revert (rollback) path.\n\n## Scope\n\nThe single atomic config change (flag + boundary) + under-enforcement verification + a\nrollback procedure. Depends on the local, GitHub Actions, Gerrit, and grandfathering stories.\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n\n- [ ] `identity.require_authenticated = true` **and** the pinned `enforce_since` (the anchor\n      from the grandfathering story) land in **one** change; `enforce_since` is written here\n      for the first time (no earlier child modifies it).\n- [ ] After the flip, `rebar verify-identity` FAILS (non-zero exit) on a new in-scope\n      unsigned/forged event — enforcement is real, not advisory.\n- [ ] **Under enforcement**, a representative write on EACH of the three surfaces (local, CI,\n      the in-scope Gerrit writer) produces `authorship: {signed: >=1}` and a `verified`\n      verdict, recorded as proof; no red pushes on `main`.\n- [ ] A documented **rollback** path exists: how to revert `identity.require_authenticated` to\n      `false` via a single fast-revert change if a writer surface unexpectedly fails\n      post-flip. [operator-attested] the rollback step is captured in the runbook."}},"env_id":"ade0f2ef-51cc-45a2-bb97-c09846cd3df5","event_type":"EDIT","timestamp":1784228121751844001,"uuid":"a517653f-c059-495c-8caf-be5cf7cb8e4f"}